						               													<description>A 4-player expansion for the co-op mode in Pixel Glory: Light and Shadow.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Sneaky Wizards adds a new Hidden Identity game mode where players have hidden objectives - some are even working for the Dungeon lord! Players earn fame for completing their objectives, and for successfully guessing what the other players roles are.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play: Each player gets a random role card. Each role has a secret objective(s). Players earn fame (victory point) for completing their hidden objectives - not from killing monsters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the end of the game, players guess what role each other player was (on paper). For each successful guess, they earn 1 additional fame.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Roles:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Hoarder (Good Role)&amp;#10;End the game with at least 3 combo points - 1 Fame.&amp;#10;Survive the dungeon - 2 Fame.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Nimble (Good Role)&amp;#10;End the game with the most health remaining - 1 Fame.&amp;#10;Survive the dungeon - 2 Fame.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Proud (Good Role)&amp;#10;End the game without defeating a 1 fame monster - 1 Fame.&amp;#10;Survive the dungeon - 2 Fame.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Traitor (2x, Evil Role)&amp;#10;The wizards are defeated - 3 Fame.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Mercenary (Neutral Role)&amp;#10;Survive the dungeon, or be the last player remaining - 1 Fame.&amp;#10;End the game with the most fame from defeated monsters - 1 Fame.&amp;#10;End the game without healing any other player - 1 Fame.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contains 10 Cards: 6 Role Cards and 4 Reference Cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
